<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Impact Story - AgriLinkHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="page-hero-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">Impact Stories</span>
        <h1>Stories of change from farms and communities</h1>
        <p>Discover how AgriLinkHub creates measurable results for farmers while improving livelihoods, food security, and local business growth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="page-hero-image">
        <img src="/images/garden-maize.svg" alt="People in the garden growing maize">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Our impact approach</h2>
      <p>AgriLinkHub delivers measurable impact by integrating agro-processing, a digital marketplace, rural transport, aggregation systems, and local partnership models. Each service streamlines the value chain and is tracked using quantitative performance data and farmer feedback.</p>
      <ul class="impact-story-list">
        <li>Set up affordable milling and value-add services for maize, cassava, and other crops</li>
        <li>Provide digital and USSD channels so farmers list produce, access prices, and receive orders</li>
        <li>Organize community logistics for farm collection, delivery, and bulk transport</li>
        <li>Build aggregation centers that link villages to schools, traders, NGOs, and retailers</li>
        <li>Engage youth and women groups, and support local agents with onboarding and training</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Quantitative impact</h2>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>14,500</h3>
          <p>Metric tonnes of grain milled and packaged through our agro-processing services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>8,700</h3>
          <p>Produce listings created by farmers using mobile app and USSD channels.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>1,250</h3>
          <p>Logistics deliveries completed by boda bodas and small trucks to collect and deliver produce.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>72</h3>
          <p>Village-level aggregation centers established to support bulk marketing and reduce supply chain fragmentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>240+</h3>
          <p>Youth and women engaged in logistics, packaging, and value-add services across local communities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Qualitative impact</h2>
      <ul class="impact-story-list">
        <li>"Milling locally gave us cleaner flour and better prices for our maize."</li>
        <li>"Through the app and USSD, buyers now find our produce faster and pay more consistently."</li>
        <li>"The logistics network makes it easy to move harvests from the village to market without extra cost."</li>
        <li>"Our aggregation center helped us sell in bulk to a school kitchen for the first time."</li>
        <li>"Young people and women now earn extra income by managing transport, packaging, and farmer support."</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Featured story: Kato's maize farm</h2>
      <p>Kato joined AgriLinkHub in early 2025. He used our milling service for his dried maize, listed his output through the USSD channel, and arranged village collection with local transport partners. His productivity rose by 40%, he secured a bulk contract with a regional buyer, and he now supports his family with stable cash flow.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Impact by service</h2>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Agro-Processing</h3>
          <p>Faster milling, packaging, and delivery helps farmers earn a quality premium and reduce post-harvest loss.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Digital Platform</h3>
          <p>Listings and price discovery keep farmers connected to buyers, while USSD ensures inclusion for all users.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Rural Logistics</h3>
          <p>Community-based transport lowers delivery costs and improves access to distant markets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Aggregation</h3>
          <p>Village centers create bulk sales opportunities and reduce fragmentation in the supply chain.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Partnerships</h3>
          <p>Youth and women groups gain income through logistics, packaging, and farmer onboarding work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>